  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, the way you asked questions with 'do' last time was perfect — it made our chat flow so smoothly. What's your pick for a movie or song tonight?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hmm, I don't watch movies often, but I like listening to Hindi songs. Maybe something by Arijit Singh? What about you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Nice choice — Arijit’s voice adds warmth to songs. I get that feeling when a melody just fits. Any particular song you enjoy the most?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Ek Zulf-e-Mehbooba by Arijit Singh is one I listen to often. The melody is very calming. Do you like music from Bollywood?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Got it — that song sounds lovely. I get how it can calm the mind. Yes, Bollywood music has a special place — the way it tells a story in just a few notes. What’s one of your favourite Bollywood scenes?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The Dilwale Dulhania Leeyan song sequence is iconic, na? The way they dance on the hillside — it's simple but so romantic. I watch it sometimes when I miss old classics."
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Same here — that hillside dance is pure magic. Old classics have a way of feeling timeless. Tell me, what’s one thing you miss the most from your childhood?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I miss playing cricket in the street with friends. Those days were so simple but full of fun. Chai aur gully cricket — best combo! These days it's all meetings and deadlines."
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Chai and gully cricket — that’s the real Indian summer. I get how meetings and deadlines can steal that joy. What’s one way you like to unwind from work stress?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I like going for evening walks, especially when it's cool. It helps me clear my head. Sometimes I think too much, and my mind needs a break! Do you have a way to unwind?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Evening walks are a great idea — fresh air and moving your body is a win. I do enjoy a quiet evening with a book when the day feels too heavy. What kind of books do you like?\""
    }
  ],
